{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1706-05_138","head":{"value":"In-promptu sur le Bain de Madame la Duchesse de Bourgogne","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", mai 1706 [tome 5], p. 138-140.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Madame la Duchesse de Bourgogne s’estant baignée, quelque temps avant l’accident qui a obligé cette Princesse de garder le lit pendant neuf jours, elle receut en sortant du bain les vers que vous allez lire, &amp; qui furent fort applaudis.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#1":{"value":"IN-PROMPTU","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"Sur le bain de Madame la Duchesse de Bourgogne.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#2"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le beau feu dont luit le Soleil,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"S’affoiblit &amp; s’esteint, quand il entre dans l’Onde :","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je sçais un Astre dans le monde,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui n’a pas un deffaut pareil.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Phebus permet qu’on le regarde,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lorsqu’il plonge en l’eau son éclat,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nul œil mortel ne se hazarde,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À voir Adelaïde en un semblable état.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Car alors elle est si brillante,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’on ne pourroit l’envisager,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans courir un plus grand danger,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que celuy d’Acteon &amp; celuy d’Erimante.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}}]}}}